N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 800.3 - Rates and charges

State Regulations

It shall be the duty of all persons, firms or corporations, making use of the facilities of the Port of Albany, to familiarize themselves
with all rates and charges promulgated by the Commission. Notes
